Text.Value: I love you.

EditorData.NodeContext: Pretends to say it very sweetly and innocently

Text.Value: Having fun, are you?
Well, it can be true, if only for tonight.
Every time I heard the Tieflings cry, I remembered how you sounded crying for me.
I'm amazed you managed to keep your mind clear enough to fight, I've been thinking about our last night together ceaselessly.
I think it's better if we leave last time as a once-off.
If you don't remember how much you enjoyed it last time, I would like to try again, until you can think of nothing else.
When I'm with you, I feel practically alive, yet I crave only to die again with you.
'A little treat'? You can do better than that.
By all means, do something less exceptional, and think of me while you're doing it.
Here's my little treat with their cheeks all flushed. You will come to my bed tonight, won't you?
So many honeyed words, as usual.
How about this one:
Very presumptuous. I'm undecided what I'll do tonight yet.
Ah, you need a bit of enticing, let me see.
You're sweet, and sillier than I thought.
I'll come find you after everyone is asleep.
And what else...?
Did these really work on Cazador's targets?
Well, they worked on you last time, didn't they?
I'll come find you after everyone is asleep.
But you... you I'll remember. Have a fine evening, dear.
I'm sure we will get another chance soon. But not right now.
In all honesty, it is a shame. That time was special to me. I've gotten on my back ten thousand times or more, and forgotten half of them.
I am, it's hard not to with you.
A little soon to say that, don't you think?
Mmmn, keep going.
Oh, I like you best. I can't help myself.
Now, as much as I relish standing around and saying all my favourite lines at you, I'd much rather we got to experience each others' full portfolio of talents once again.
I'll come find you later.
Every part of your perfect body whispers temptation - it's as if the Gods made you just to ruin me.
I'll come find you later.
Is that the best you can do?
Oh I don't know. It might be worth it.
All these accolades from the Tieflings are nothing compared to the sound of my name, cried from your lips.
We can't have that, can we? It would be very dangerous.
On second thought, maybe not tonight.
I'll be waiting.
You don't have to ask twice.
Ah ha, but a rather beautiful lie, nonetheless.
I look forward to the day. Meanwhile, my hunger for you will only deepen.

EditorData.logicalname: NOT AVAILABLE AS PARTY ROMANCE PARTNER

Text.Value: I'd love that, Astarion, but you know I can't. I'd burn you alive.
I'm just busy tonight.
Sorry, I may want to spend some time with someone else.

EditorData.logicalname: IF AT PARTY AND HAS OTHER NIGHT PARTNER

Text.Value: I can go on all night with the flattery, but is that really all you want?
I'll be in quite a spot of mortal peril if you let me keep distracting myself dreaming instead of doing.
How about if I said these little words... Everyone's favourite...
I don't think I really want this.
Well, well, excuse me while I die of a broken heart.
Not half as sweet as when I tasted you.
You'd be lying.
Oh, I certainly can, it would be my pleasure.
Hmm, let me give it another go:

Synopsis:
Second time Astarion propositions the player to sleep with him - optional CRD between his act 1 and act 2 critical path romance scenes.
The player starts to realise Astarion might have been just playing an act to seduce them the whole time, and that his affection for them might not be genuine. Bridges the gap before he confesses this in his act 2 romance, and says he wants to stop manipulating people and have a real relationship.
Could either be triggered at the party, or any time before the act 2 scene, as long as you've slept with him before.
If player agrees to meet up with Astarion later, it will show them meeting up at the bedroll when the player clicks to rest automatically if it's not at the party, if no other overnight scene is queued. If it's at the party, the player has to choose at the bedroll menu to meet up with him.
